msgstr "2026年4月18日"

#: app/templates/index.html:116
msgid "May 29, 2026"
msgstr "2026年5月29日"

#: app/templates/index.html:124
msgid "June 8–9, 2026"
msgstr "2026年6月8日至9日"

#: app/templates/index.html:139
msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "参与进来"

#: app/templates/index.html:140
msgid "Explore the gallery, meet the artists, and share your own work."
msgstr "探索画廊，认识艺术家，并分享您自己的作品。"

#: app/templates/index.html:142
msgid ""
"Discover new exhibitions, learn about the artists behind each piece, and "
"submit your artwork to be part of our growing collection."
msgstr "发现新的展览，了解每件作品背后的艺术家，并提交您的作品，成为我们不断成长的收藏的一部分。"

#: app/templates/index.html:147
msgid "Explore Gallery"
msgstr "浏览画廊"

#: app/templates/painting.html:30
msgid "View All Works"
msgstr "查看所有作品"

#: app/templates/submit.html:7
msgid "Submit Your Artwork"
msgstr "提交您的作品"

#: app/templates/submit.html:8
msgid ""
"Fill in the form below. Our team will review your submission and be in "
"touch."
msgstr "请填写下列表单。我们的团队将审核您的投稿，并与您联系。"

#: app/templates/submit.html:22
msgid ""
"Thank you! Your submission has been received. We will review it and get "
"back to you."
msgstr "感谢您！您的投稿已收到。我们会进行审核并与您联系。"

