msgstr "我们会尽快与您联系"

#: app/templates/thank_you.html:22
msgid ""
"Thank you for contacting Global Art Gallery. Our team reviews enquiries "
"during business hours and usually replies within 1 to 2 business days."
msgstr "感谢您联系全球艺术画廊。我们的团队会在营业时间内处理咨询，通常会在1至2个工作日内回复。"

